{"word":"ἀγνώμων","slug":"ἀγνώμων","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀγνώμων</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:γνώμη'><el>γνώμη</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>ill-judging, senseless</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-όνως</el>, <i>senselessly</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>headstrong, reckless, arrogant</i>, (in <a href='S:Comparative'>comp.</a> <el>-ονέστερος</el>) <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; in <a href='S:Superlative'>Sup.</a>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>unfeeling, unkind, hardhearted</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>of things, <i>senseless, brute</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschines'>Aeschin.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}